    "Procedural_Checklist": {
      "text": "Consent in chart\nPIV with fluids running\nETCO2 and NC connected to patient\nAirway preparation\nSuction with Yankauer attached\nBVM attached to wall oxygen\nOral/nasal airways\nMac/Miller blades\nET tubes with stylets\nMeds at bedside\nSedation Meds\nNarcan\n0.4mg if opioid being used, not drawn up\nEpinephrine\n, cardiac syringe (1:10,000) unopened and 10 cc NS Flush with needle\nGlycopyrrolate\n, 1 vial; not drawn up\nStrongly consider child life",
      "subsections": {},
      "tables": [],
      "links": [
        {
          "text": "Narcan",
