      "subsections": {
        "Oral_Sedation": {
          "text": "Consider if only sedation without analgesia required\nMidazolam\n0.5-1mg/kg PO 10-20min prior to procedure\nChloral hydrate\n50-75mg/kg PO 30min prior to procedure\nMay give additional 25-50mg/kg PO x 1 after 30min if needed\nMidazolam\n0.5-1 mg/kg, Max 20mg (10-20 min before procddure)\nChloral hydrate\n50-70mg/kg PO 30 min prior to procedure, then repeat 25-50 mg/kg x 1 in 30 min if needed (max 1g/day infants; 2g/day older children)",
          "tables": []
        },
